values:
- primary carbon is internally mixed with secondary aerosol by merging the primary carbon mode with the accumulation mode; 
- the  coarse  dust  and  sea  salt  modes  are merged  into  a single coarse mode; 
- the fine dust and sea salt modes are similarly merged with the accumulation mode;
- sulfate  is  partially  neutralized  by  ammonium  in the form of NH4HSO4, so that ammonium is effectively pre-scribed and NH3 is not simulated.
